✅ COMPLETED: Sales Management System with Test Data

## Implemented Features:

### Backend (Django):
✅ Customer Management (CRUD)
✅ Invoice Management (CRUD) 
✅ Quotation Management (CRUD)
✅ Receipt Management (CRUD)
✅ Models with proper relationships
✅ Django Admin interface
✅ Auto-generated invoice/quotation/receipt numbers
✅ Financial analytics and reporting
✅ Accounts receivable aging analysis

### Frontend (Bootstrap UI):
✅ Responsive dashboard with financial metrics
✅ Customer list, create, edit, delete, detail views
✅ Invoice list, create, edit, delete, detail views  
✅ Quotation list, create, edit, delete, detail views
✅ Receipt list, create, edit, delete, detail views
✅ Search and filter functionality
✅ Professional Bootstrap-based UI
✅ Comprehensive analytics page
✅ Outstanding receivables tracking

### Key Features:
✅ Convert quotations to invoices
✅ Track invoice payments with receipts
✅ Customer relationship tracking
✅ Payment status monitoring
✅ Professional admin interface
✅ Financial dashboards and KPIs
✅ Accounts receivable aging reports
✅ Payment method analytics
✅ Monthly trend analysis

### Test Data Generated:
✅ 60 realistic customers (Arabic & English names)
✅ 100+ products/services (IT, consulting, Arabic services)
✅ 100 quotations with various statuses
✅ 150 invoices (some from quotations, some standalone)
✅ 147 payment receipts with realistic scenarios
✅ $3.97M in total invoiced amount
✅ $2.48M in collections (62.4% collection rate)
✅ $1.49M in outstanding receivables
✅ Multiple payment methods and aging scenarios

## Access Information:
- Web Interface: http://localhost:8010/
- Admin Panel: http://localhost:8010/admin/
- Analytics: http://localhost:8010/analytics/
- Username: admin
- Password: admin123

## Management Commands:
```bash
# Generate test data
python manage.py populate_test_data --customers 60 --quotations 100 --invoices 150 --clear

# Generate receivables report
python manage.py receivables_report
```

